    "data": [
        {
            "title": "紅磡男途人捱私家車撞 昏迷送院搶救 男司機涉危駕被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"紅磡男途人捱私家車撞，昏迷送院搶救，男司機涉危駕被捕。黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a2aa163325c2c6ca067be75c41756f0f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051504281361729.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">紅磡男途人捱私家車撞，昏迷送院搶救，男司機涉危駕被捕。黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>紅磡發生車禍。今日（15日）凌晨近3時，一輛白色寶馬私家車，沿戴亞街行駛期間，駛至紅磡邨對開時，疑收掣不及撞向一名男途人。救護員趕至現場，該名非洲籍男途人昏迷被送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。\n\n</p>\n<p>消息指，事發時白色寶馬沿戴亞街向海逸豪園方向行駛，途至紅磡邨對開時，突然有一名男子在路中出現，私家車收掣不及，右車頭將途人撞倒，私家車再駛前近30米後停下。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249177/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地上留有血迹。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61266f963669c503f219ebc5acc04b4f/2025-05/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-05-15-04-04-38_002.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地上留有血迹。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249178/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車側鏡及擋風玻璃損毀。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f70728fdc735faaaf8e06403fc942ee7/2025-05/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-05-15-04-04-45_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車側鏡及擋風玻璃損毀。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249179/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寶馬撞傷男途人後，駛前30米停低。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c112c7f2913fb49d8cdfc77e8ffd3e7/2025-05/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-05-15-04-05-10_008.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶馬撞傷男途人後，駛前30米停低。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249180/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b6095c05d9eab54c4343df0b77255bb0/2025-05/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-05-15-04-05-15_009.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249181/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男司機涉危駕被捕。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32ca3223813da3771b03fc0db2b5722c/2025-05/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-05-15-04-05-25_012.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男司機涉危駕被捕。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方初步調查，男司機接受酒精呼氣測試顯示有度數，但未有超標。警方以涉嫌「危險駕駛導致他人身體受嚴重傷害」拘捕寶馬男司機。就現場所見，寶馬私家車擋風玻璃龜裂，右側鏡損毀，地上留下屬於傷者的血迹；男司機父母事後到場了解。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068988/即時-港聞-紅磡男途人捱私家車撞-昏迷送院搶救-男司機涉危駕被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 04:41:31",
